title: RV Lot available, South Olympia
posting_body: Want to offer our RV space.
You must have your own RV.
It says one bedroom bc CL wouldn't allow us to post w/o putting something.
Want ONE quiet responsible respectful adult.
No flakes, want.
Prefer no guests except perhaps on very RARE occasions one guest.
Likely we could discuss some sort of cover for winter time for your RV,  if you would like that.
Super lovely quiet acreage setting in South Olympia.
We could be open to you doing work (typically outside type things, weeding, removing invasive plants , etc).
However, we would need you to pay the rent and we reimburse you after the fact for work.
We have enough work that you could live rent free IF you work.
We have found that is the BEST  you pay the rent and we pay you for your work.
Indoor pet in your RV is fine.
We do NOT want any cat or dog ever LOOSE on the property.
Cats kill birds, etc and dont want the cat burying their poop outside and absolutely do NOT want dog poop NOT picked IMMEDIATELY
so NO dog off leash EVER.
One pet
and it must be current on vaccinations, spay/neutered.
It is on acreage, but we live there too.
You can email us with your phone number, but we wont be showing till after Aug 8th.
Thank you kindly
